Place your audio files here before running the scripts.

REQUIRED INPUT FILES
──────────────────────────────────────
  Conference.wav   — first audio signal (any mono or stereo .wav)
  Sports.wav       — second audio signal (any mono or stereo .wav)

GENERATED OUTPUT FILES (created automatically by the scripts)
──────────────────────────────────────
  fdmSignal.wav           — FDM composite signal (output of transmitter.m)
  if_signal1.wav          — IF-filtered signal 1 (output of receiver.m)
  if_signal2.wav          — IF-filtered signal 2 (output of receiver.m)
  demodulated_signal1.wav — recovered audio signal 1 (44.1 kHz)
  demodulated_signal2.wav — recovered audio signal 2 (44.1 kHz)

NOTE: All .wav files are excluded from version control via .gitignore
because they are large binary files. Add your own input files locally.
